		"description": "<p dir=\"ltr\">You have a touch of psychic ability that you can use in a limited, but useful way. You gain the following benefits:</p>\n<ul>\n<li dir=\"ltr\" aria-level=\"1\">\n<p dir=\"ltr\" role=\"presentation\">You gain a single psi die that is always a d4 and does not grow in size.&nbsp;</p>\n</li>\n<li dir=\"ltr\" aria-level=\"1\">\n<p dir=\"ltr\" role=\"presentation\">Choose the Empathetic, Kinesthetic, or Telepathic discipline. You can also enter psychic focus as a second-level esper with the chosen discipline.</p>\n</li>\n<li dir=\"ltr\" aria-level=\"1\">\n<p dir=\"ltr\" role=\"presentation\">You gain a single Noetic of your choice from the esper class. You must meet any prerequisites the noetic has to select it.</p>\n</li>\n</ul>",
